    14→ * Delegates all extraction logic to {@link EnrichmentPipeline}, which in turn
    15→ * delegates to every registered {@link ITextEnrichment} via the
    16→ * {@link TextEnrichmentManager}.
    17→ *
    18→ * This service is responsible only for:
